channel.title: Trail To Final X (updated on July 16th)
channel.description:
[size=16pt][b]Trail To Final X[/b][/size]
[b]Yep![/b] [i]I'm setting up this thread so people can get hyped for my new server, Trail To Final X.[/i] [b]It's the last[/b] [i]Trail server in the series to be made (then I'll make new ones under different names), so I'm trying to make this one my best yet.[/i] [b]I will be buying[/b] [i]2 gigs or more of RAM so that I can hold many more people - hopefully reaching 190+.[/i]
[b]TESTING IS DONE. I WILL KEEP YOU GUYS INFORMED USING THIS THREAD.[/b]
[b]- Done[/b]
[ul][li]New starting point[/li] [li]Full specials[/li] [li]2 dungeons[/li] [li]HUGE AMOUNTS OF SKILLS (see below)[/li] [li]My own skillcapes[/li] [li]377 client with sprites etc.[/li] [li]Lots of shops[/li] [li]Sweet PKing[/li] [li]Rares are difficult[/li] [li]Added a test quest[/li] [li]98% Barrows[/li] [li]An amazing hand-coded Jad game[/li] [li]The server is difficult[/li] [li]Crystal bow hits hard, but not too hard[/li] [li]Added a Dagganoth Chamber - God Armors[/li] [li]Changed server's economy[/li] [li]Added soe discontinued items[/li][/ul]
[b]- Skills[/b]
[ul][li]Cooking[/li] [li]Fishing[/li] [li]Woodcutting[/li] [li]Thieving[/li] [li]Crafting[/li] [li]Mining[/li] [li]Smithing[/li] [li]Runecrafting[/li] [li]Herblore[/li][/ul]
